      <title>美国牛群数量降至 74 年来最低水平，牛肉价格将维持高位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/beef-set-to-stay-pricey-as-us-cattle-herd-falls-to-74-year-low</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于牧场干燥和牛肉需求旺盛，美国牛肉数量连续第五年无法增长，导致美国牛肉供应量降至 1951 年以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/beef-set-to-stay-pricey-as-us-cattle-herd-falls-to-74-year-low</guid>
